plyTime":"2021-05-04T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"咪亂share，小心俾人告"},{"pid":"255294194984ba607bee44149febce5fea29c4f9","tid":2514823,"uid":258550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"文學放得開 2018 唔見咗好多😭"},{"pid":"d8ce570e2292aafc0798148f5de5201b3f9c1677","tid":2514823,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"推..............."}],"pinned":{"pid":"34487130a3bde7fb25cd0b54f3560ea74329ee0b","tid":2514823,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"歡迎加入Backup師行列！<br />\n<br />\n總之所有yt冇嘅都去 <a href=\"http://podcast.rthk.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpodcast.rthk.hk&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=de33a99f\" target=\"_blank\">podcast.rthk.hk</a> 睇<br />\n<br />\n請參考以下Google Doc，入面有不同影片進度同教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1I3yYU2CTjlDt39xOZaSf7Qjj87eArrqEDp4897SaaSw/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1I3yYU2CTjlDt39xOZaSf7Qjj87eArrqEDp4897SaaSw%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=ba87b820\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1I3yYU2CTjlDt39xOZaSf7Qjj87eArrqEDp4897SaaSw/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n另有整理資源用大Google Sheet，backup完可以幫手整理：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=946262fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗YouTube之外，可以到RTHK Podcast官網backup<br />\n有啲片可能YouTube del咗，但係官網未！<br />\n<a href=\"https://podcast.rthk.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcast.rthk.hk%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=4368dad1\" target=\"_blank\">https://podcast.rthk.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n提提大家Podcast最好講清楚係Podcast Video定真。淨係得聲嘅Podcast<br />\n<br />\nTUTORIAL 教學 (無圖)<br />\n===========================<br />\n1. YouTube下載可以用youtube-dl + lbry publish<br />\n<a href=\"https://odysee.com/@code:a/kit:d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fodysee.com%2F%40code%3Aa%2Fkit%3Ad&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=7e88c541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://odysee.com/@code:a/kit:d</a><br />\n//This could be very useful if you lost access to a video or if you want to backup something and you don't have the youtube sync turned on. It also works as a limited version of of youtube-dl if you want to download .mp4 or .mp3   To sum up youtube-dl + lbry publish //<br />\n<br />\n2. Curl command批量下載港台Podcast 教學<br />\nI. 用chrome是旦搵一個channel(右click禁&rdquo;檢查&rdquo;)<br />\nII. 入到一版可以睇到晒所有片<br />\nIII. 禁最先果條片(eg. 20200101), 對住下載果個制禁&rdquo;檢查&rdquo;<br />\nIV. 你會見到隔離dev tool出左條link, 先記低呢條link<br />\nV. 開terminal，用mac機做demo。先係terminal到打 &ldquo;pwd&rdquo;(present working directory)，會出番你依家係邊個folder，d片就係down係果度<br />\n<br />\nVI. 佢20170101果條片既pattern係由S01000001開始，<br />\npath: <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000001.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01000001.mp4&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=35ade53c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000001.mp4</a> <br />\n<br />\n仲係...2017S01000既pattern既最後一條片應該係10月26<br />\npath : <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000205.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01000205.mp4&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=51b94459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000205.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n所以我地download 左呢個pattern既片先。作用： download由20170101 － 20171026既片<br />\ncurl -O <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000[001-205].mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01000%5B001-205%5D.mp4&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=68aed741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000[001-205].mp4</a> <br />\n<br />\nVII. 如果你直接禁2017年最後一條片就發覺佢既pattern唔同左。跟住我就搵埋下一個pattern既第一條片係咩（好似係2017年既10月27定28號）<br />\n<br />\n新pattern係由&rdquo;<a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01100001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01100001&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=f850feba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01100001</a> 去到 <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01100055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01100055&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=51c53cc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01100055</a> 。<br />\n去番terminal果到輸入以下既command: <br />\ncurl -O <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S011000[01-55].mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S011000%5B01-55%5D.mp4&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=4014107f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S011000[01-55].mp4</a>  <br />\n<br />\nVIII. 完成。你應該會見到佢down緊，不過係會有d慢。我發覺有d係會down左但係播唔到，有時間可以double check, 感謝！！"}}